Sys::Info::Driver::Windows
==========================

Windows driver for Sys::Info.

Read the module's POD for documentation.
See the tests for examples.

INSTALLATION

You'll need a C compiler to install this module, as it has some XS code. MSVC6
and MinGW compilers are recommended. To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

or under Windows:

   perl Makefile.PL
   nmake
   nmake test
   nmake install

DEPENDENCIES

Only installs and works on Windows.

